\\
g\left( 0 \right) =0,g'\left( x \right) =f'\left( x \right) +e^{-x}=\frac{x}{x+1}e^{-x}\geqslant 0     {\color[RGB]{0, 0, 240} //g'\left( x \right) \geqslant 0\Rightarrow g\left( x \right) \text{单调递增，可求出最小值}.}
