QuestionTxt:
若正项级数$\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{a_n}$与正项级数$\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{b_n}$都收敛,证明下列级数收敛:
$\left( 1 \right) \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\sqrt{a_nb_n}}$;
$\left( 2 \right) \sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\frac{\sqrt{a_n}}{n}}.$

AnswerTxt:
$$
\\
\text{【解析】}
\\
{\color[rgb]{240, 0, 0} \text{方法一：直接法}}
\\
\text{由于}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{收敛，则}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_{n+1}}\text{也收敛，从而有}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left( u_n+u_{n+1} \right)}\text{收敛，故应选}\left( \mathrm{D} \right) 
\\
{\color[rgb]{240, 0, 0} \text{方法二：排除法}}
\\
\,\,\text{选项}A\text{：}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left| \left( -1 \right) ^n\frac{u_n}{n} \right|}=\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left| \frac{u_n}{n} \right|}
\\
\text{由于}\left| \frac{u_n}{n} \right|<\left| u_n \right|, \text{因此，如果级数}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left| u_n \right|}\text{收敛，则}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left( -1 \right) ^n}\frac{u_n}{n}\text{绝对收敛，}
\\
\text{题目已知}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{收敛，并未讲明是否是绝对收敛，因此，}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left| u_n \right|}\text{不一定收敛}
\\
\text{当然，若已知}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{为正项级数，则}A\text{选项时正确的，题目未说明}A\text{是正项级数，因此，}\left( \mathrm{A} \right) \text{选项不正确}
\\
\text{例如：令}u_n=\frac{\left( -1 \right) ^n}{\ln n}\text{，由交错级数的菜布尼茨准则知}\sum\limits_{n=2}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{收敛，但}\sum\limits_{n=2}^{\infty}{\left( -1 \right) ^n}\frac{u_n}{n}=\sum\limits_{n=2}^{\infty}{\frac{1}{n\ln n}}\text{发散}
\\
{\color[rgb]{0, 0, 240} // \sum\limits_{n=2}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{条件收敛}\begin{cases}
	\lim\limits_{n\rightarrow \infty} u_n=\lim\limits_{n\rightarrow \infty} \frac{1}{\ln n}=0\\
	u_{n+1}-u_n=\frac{1}{\ln \left( n+1 \right)}-\frac{1}{\ln n}=\frac{\ln n-\ln \left( n+1 \right)}{\ln \left( n+1 \right) \ln n}<0\left( n\rightarrow \infty \right)\\
\end{cases}}
\\
{\color[rgb]{0, 0, 240} }/{\color[rgb]{0, 0, 240} / \sum\limits_{n=2}^{\infty}{\frac{1}{n\ln n}}\text{发散：根据积分判别法，}\int_2^{+\infty}{\frac{1}{x\ln x}\mathrm{d}x}=\left. \frac{\ln ^2x}{2} \right|_{2}^{+\infty}=+\infty ,\text{发散，}}
\\
{\color[rgb]{0, 0, 240} \sum\limits_{n=2}^{\infty}{\frac{1}{n\ln n}}\text{与反常积分}\int_2^{+\infty}{\frac{1}{x\ln x}\mathrm{d}x}\text{具有相同的敛散性，因此}\sum\limits_{n=2}^{\infty}{\frac{1}{n\ln n}}\text{发散}}
\\
\,\,\text{选项}B\text{：与选项}A\text{已知，}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{不一定是绝对收敛}
\\
\text{例如：令}u_n=\frac{\left( -1 \right) ^{n-1}}{\sqrt{n}},\text{显然}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{收敛，但}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_{n}^{2}}=\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\frac{1}{n}}\text{发散，则}\left( \mathrm{B} \right) \text{不正确}
\\
\,\,\text{设}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{收敛，则}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left( u_{2n-1}-u_{2n} \right)}\text{不定}
\\
\text{例如：令}u_n=\frac{\left( -1 \right) ^{n-1}}{\sqrt{n}}\text{，}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{u_n}\text{条件收敛}
\\
\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left( u_{2n-1}-u_{2n} \right)}=\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left( \frac{1}{\sqrt{2n-1}}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{2n}} \right)}
\\
\text{由于}\frac{1}{\sqrt{2n-1}}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{2n}}\geqslant \frac{1}{\sqrt{2n}}+\frac{1}{\sqrt{2n}}=\frac{\sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{n}}\text{，而}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\frac{\sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{n}}}\text{发散}  {\color[rgb]{0, 0, 240} // \text{根据}p\text{级数性质}}
\\
\text{则}\sum\limits_{n=1}^{\infty}{\left( u_{2n-1}-u_{2n} \right)}\text{发散，则}\left( \mathrm{C} \right) \text{不正确，故应选}\left( \mathrm{D} \right) 
